extends AbstractParticipantFilter

InChIFilter â€“ 2011.08.14 Filters an InChIParticpant for those which are not H2O, H+, O2, CO2. The default rejections can be removed by using the removeRejection(InChI) method and using the public InChI attributes InChIFilter.HYDRON, InChIFilter.WATER, InChIFilter.CARBON_DIOXIDE and InChIFilter.DIOXYGEN
